#: lutris/runners/easyrpg.py:75
msgid "Patches"
msgstr "Lappar"

#: lutris/runners/easyrpg.py:77
msgid ""
"Instead of autodetecting patches used by this game, force emulation of certain patches.\n"
"\n"
"Available patches:\n"
"<b>common-this</b>: \"This Event\" in common events<b>dynrpg</b>: DynRPG patch by Cherry<b>key-patch</b>: Key Patch by Ineluki<b>maniac</b>: Maniac Patch by BingShan<b>pic-unlock</b>: Pictures are not blocked by messages<b>rpg2k3-cmds</b>: Support all RPG Maker 2003 event commands in any version of the engine\n"
"\n"
"You can provide multiple patches or use 'none' to disable all engine patches."
msgstr ""
"Istället för att autodetektera patchar som används av detta spel, tvinga fram emulering av vissa patchar.\n"
"\n"
"Tillgängliga patchar:\n"
"<b>common-this</b>: \"Denna händelse\" i vanliga händelser<b>dynrpg</b>: DynRPG patch av Cherry<b>key-patch</b>: Key Patch av Ineluki<b>maniac</b>: Maniac Patch av BingShan<b>pic-unlock</b>: Bilder blockeras inte av meddelanden<b>rpg2k3-cmds</b>: Stödjer alla RPG Maker 2003-händelsekommandon i alla versioner av motorn\n"
"\n"
"Du kan ange flera patchar eller använda 'none' för att inaktivera alla motorpatchar."

#: lutris/runners/easyrpg.py:92 lutris/runners/scummvm.py:276
msgid "Language"
msgstr "Språk"

#: lutris/runners/easyrpg.py:93
